Use framework-native patterns: Elysia plugins, htmx attributes (hx-get, hx-post, hx-swap, hx-target), DaisyUI component classes, Prisma client extensions. No legacy shims or polyfills.

For Pixi.js, Three.js, HuggingFace Transformers, Playwright, and Biome (not in this static doc set), use the Context7 MCP server per context7.mdc.
